<h2>What makes MelonCube <span></span></h2>
<p class="mobile home-intro">Our goal at MelonCube is to provide gamers killer performance hosting with 100% uptime that meets even the highest requirements, whilst maintaining an affordable price. We are committed to raising the bar in the game server industry. Join us and experience the difference today!</p>
<div class="row text-center">
<div class="col-md-4">
<img src="assets/img/icons/cpu.svg" alt="High Performance Minecraft Server Hosting">
<h3>High Performance</h3>
<p>At MelonCube, we utilise only the highest performance enterprise server hardware to optimise our infrastructure for the best minecraft hosting experience in the industry. <a href="c/specs/">Our Hardware</a>.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<img src="assets/img/icons/uptime.svg" alt="100% Uptime Minecraft Server Hosting">
<h3>100% Uptime</h3>
<p>Many hosts make bold "claims" about uptime, but usually, this is just marketing and promotion. Uptime is something that we're absolutely fanatical and extremely proud about.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<img src="assets/img/icons/ssd.svg" alt="SSD Minecraft Hosting">
<h3>Solid State Drives</h3>
<p>Lightning fast Solid State Drives (SSD) ensure guaranteed accelerated Minecraft world loading and an essential lag-free experience for you, and your valuable players.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row text-center">
<div class="col-md-4">
<img src="assets/img/icons/delivery.svg" alt="Instant Minecraft Server Hosting">
<h3>Instant Activation</h3>
<p>Why wait for your Minecraft server after ordering? We deliver your server instantly after you finalise your order so that you can get started without any delays.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<img src="assets/img/icons/ddos.svg" alt="DDoS Protected Minecraft Server Hosting">
<h3>DDoS Protection</h3>
<p>Our Minecraft servers are protected by our 480Gbps DDoS protection and automatic mitigation systems which allow us to guarantee unbeatable 100% uptime! <a href="c/ddos/">DDoS Protection</a>.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<img src="assets/img/icons/multicraft.svg" alt="Multicraft Minecraft Server Hosting">
<h3>Power Control Panel</h3>
<p>Our Minecraft servers are powered by the easy-to-use Multicraft (2.0) control panel which provides clients with a powerful, but simple to use control solution.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row text-center">
<div class="col-md-4">
<img src="assets/img/icons/users.svg" alt="Multi-User Minecraft Server Hosting">
<h3>Multi-User Support</h3>
<p>You don't play alone, and managing your server shouldn't be done alone either. Our control panel allows multiple accounts so that others can have access to the control panel!</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<img src="assets/img/icons/connection.svg" alt="Fast Connection Minecraft Server Hosting">
<h3>1Gbps Connection</h3>
<p>Your servers are connected to the internet through premium bandwidth carriers and a 1Gbps connections - keeping your Minecraft hosting latency at its lowest.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
<img src="assets/img/icons/free.svg" alt="Free Buycraft Ultimate and Free Enjin Advanced">
<h3>Free Perks!</h3>
<p>We don't <em>nickel and dime</em>. You get free: unlimited slots, MySQL database, support, 30 days Buycraft Ultimate, 45 days Enjin Advanced and 30 days Minetrends Lite!</p>
</div>
</div>
<h4 class="text-center">...and many more features!</h4>
</div>
